headline: Netflix, Goldman Sachs, J&J: Earnings to Watch This Week
summary: Earnings season takes off this week led by U.S. banks. JPMorgan Chase, Goldman Sachs and others. Big non-financial companies including Johnson & Johnson, Netflix and PepsiCo are also on the way. Here are the highlights of who is reporting, and the expected approximate release times.

headline: Raymond James Upgrades U.S. Bancorp (USB) Stock to Strong Buy
summary: U.S. Bancorp (NYSE:USB) is one of the Best Large Cap Value Stocks to Invest In.
